description:
Joe Pass at the Guitar Workshop, hosted by Bruce Clarke in Melbourne, Australia in 1981
1.Bass parts and moving lines
2.Cherokee
3.General Comments
4.Guitarists or Musicians
5.How High The Moon (numbering error in video)
6.I'm Confessin' (analysis)
7.I'm Confessin' (duet)
8.Unlocking the chord forms
fulltitle: Joe Pass seminar at the Guitar Workshop pt 2 (audio only)
